<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    {{>nav}}
    <div class="product_info_container mx-auto">
        <div class="product_info_main">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 product_info_img mx-auto">
                    <div class="product_main_img">
                        <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/December2021/hoddie24.jpg" style = "width: 600px" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="product_side_img">
                        <div class="side-img">
                            <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/December2021/hoddie24.jpg" class = "show-up" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div class="side-img">
                            <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/December2021/hoddie26.jpg" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 product_description">
                    <div class="product_title">
                        Áo Polo nam Café
                    </div>
                    <div class="product_rating">
                        <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                        <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                        <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                        <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                        <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                        <span class = "normal-span review-rating-label">| 100</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="product-price">
                        <span class = "currentPrice me-3 price">
                            299.000đ
                        </span>
                        <span class = "price_before_sale me-3 price text-muted">
                            <del>329.000đ</del>
                        </span>
                        <span class = "percent_sale text-danger price me-3">
                            -10%
                        </span>
                        <br>
                        <div class = "btn btn-outline-primary doubleSale mt-3">
                            Mua 2 chỉ còn 289k/chiếc
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span>Màu sắc: </span>
                        <input type="text" class = "color-input trans-input fw-bold" disabled>
                        <br>
                        <div class = "d-flex color-div">
                            <div class = "color-list">
                                <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/November2021/4-4_56_80x80.jpg" value = "Đen"  alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class = "color-list">
                                <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/November2021/3-4-copy_37_80x80.jpg" value = "Xanh navy" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class = "color-list">
                                <img src="https://mcdn2-coolmate.cdn.vccloud.vn/uploads/November2021/5-3-copy_79_80x80.jpg" value = "Xám" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <span>Kích thước: </span>
                        <input type="text" class = "trans-input size-input fw-bold" disabled>
                        <div class="d-flex size-div">
                            <div class="size-list" value = "S">
                                S
                            </div>
                            <div class="size-list" value = "M">
                                M
                            </div>
                            <div class="size-list" value = "L">
                                L
                            </div>
                            <div class="size-list" value = "XL">
                                XL
                            </div>
                            <div class="size-list" value = "2XL">
                                2XL
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class = "d-flex cart-div">
                            <div class = "quantity-div d-flex">
                                <span class = "fw-bold operator minus"> - </span>
                                <input type="text" value = "1" class = " fw-bold trans-input quantity-input" disabled>
                                <span class = "fw-bold operator plus"> + </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="confirmOrder-div">
                                Thêm vào giỏ hàng
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="features">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                            Đổi trả cực dễ chỉ cần số điện thoại
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                          Miễn phí vận chuyển cho đơn trên 300k
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                            60 ngày đổi trả hàng vì bất cứ lý do gì
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                            Tổng đài hỗ trợ 1900.88.88.88 24/24
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                            Hỗ trợ thanh toán trên nhiều hình thức
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <div class="feature">
                                        <div class = "feature-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="feature-title">
                                            Hoàn trả tiền trong vòng 24h
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class = "product_info_description">
            <div class="product_title">
                Chi tiết sản phẩm
            </div>
            <div class="product_description_box mx-auto">
                <p>Đây sẽ là chiếc áo đầu tiên trong tủ đồ của bạn với chất liệu bền vững và thân thiện với môi trường! 
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product_info_review">
            <div class="product_title">
                Đánh giá
            </div>
            <div class="review-header pl-50 d-flex">
                <select class = "select-review">
                    <option value = "none">Đánh giá</option>
                    <option value="1-star">1 sao</option>
                    <option value="2-star">2 sao</option>
                    <option value="3-star">3 sao</option>
                    <option value="4-star">4 sao</option>
                    <option value="5-star">5 sao</option>
                </select>
                <p>
                    Bình luận
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="review-comment pl-50 d-flex">
                <div class="rating-star">
                    <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                    <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                    <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                    <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                    <i class = "review-rating-star is-active"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="rating-comment">
                    <div class="user_comment fw-bold">
                        Lê Công Nam
                    </div>
                    <div class="colorAndSizeBought">
                        Xám tro / S
                    </div>
                    <div class="main_comment">
                        <p>Vải tốt</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="time_comment">
                        20.12.2021
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{>footer}}
</body>
</html>